> A modern CLI tool that instantly scaffolds **production-ready FastAPI** project structures with best practices, interactive prompts, and customizable templates.

---

## Overview

`fastapi-initializr` helps you bootstrap **FastAPI** projects in seconds â€” similar to how `create-react-app` or `spring initializr` works.  
It provides a simple, interactive CLI that sets up a clean, well-structured FastAPI project with everything you need to start coding right away.

---

## Features

âœ… Interactive CLI prompts using [Questionary](https://github.com/tmbo/questionary)  
âœ… Beautiful, colorized terminal experience with [Colorama](https://pypi.org/project/colorama/)  
âœ… Built-in spinner and progress indicators with [Yaspin](https://pypi.org/project/yaspin/)  
âœ… Instantly generates recommended folder structures for **FastAPI**  
âœ… Cross-platform â€” works on Linux, macOS, and Windows  

